Class AbstractTargetedConstraints<T extends IValueConstraintSupport>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.model.common.constraint.AbstractTargetedConstraints<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the constraint container
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConstraintSupport, ITargetedConstaints, IValueConstraintSupport
    public abstract class AbstractTargetedConstraints<T extends IValueConstraintSupport>
extends Object
implements ITargetedConstaints
    Provides an base implementation for a set of external constraints that target a given definition using a target Metapath expression.
